cks can be used to label axes or categories, decorate the activity, or provide additional information.\n\n## Published and Unpublished activities\n\nWhen published, users can take the activity and submit responses.\nWhen not published, an activity\'s contents can be edited and configured.\nAlways unpublish a visual activity before making changes.',
